Package: scads
Title: Single-Cell ATAC-seq Disease Scoring via Topic Modeling and S-LDSC
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Li", "Yu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "li.yu@dartmouth.edu"),
    person("Siming", "Zhao", role = "aut"))
Description: Computes per-cell disease relevance scores from single-cell
    ATAC-seq data and GWAS summary statistics. The pipeline fits a topic
    model (via fastTopics), creates topic-specific genomic annotations,
    runs stratified LD score regression (S-LDSC), and combines enrichment
    estimates with cell-level topic loadings to produce a cell-level
    disease score.
